articles.author: ROD McGUIRK Associated Press
articles.title: Australia’s High Court dismisses Russia’s bid for injunction to halt its embassy’s eviction - ABC News
articles.description: Australia’s highest court has dismissed Russia’s application for an injunction that would have halted the eviction of its embassy from a site in the capital, Canberra
